data.description: Rare 1 owner 1972 built home on 10.8 acres in Brainerd City Limits. Custom built 3 bedroom 2 bath home with cathedral ceilings, wood beams, wood fireplace, built in range, wall oven, and unfinished basement. Enjoy the country setting overlooking the 10.8 acres from the 3 decks! 2 car attached garage and 30x60 pole building/barn. Rare opportunity for hobby farm in city limits as it is grandfathered in with fenced pasture areas. Horses and most livestock ok! Great development opportunity as well.
